Doubt;;78;;79;;PG-13;;In 1964 the winds of change are sweeping through Sister Aloysius' (Meryl Streep) St. Nicholas school. Father Flynn (Philip Seymour Hoffman), a charismatic priest, is advocating reform of the school's strict customs, and the first black student has just been accepted. When a fellow nun (Amy Adams) tells Sister Aloysius that Father Flynn may be paying too much personal attention to the student, Sister Aloysius begins a personal crusade against the priest -- despite her lack of evidence.;;Drama;;John Patrick Shanley;;2008;;Meryl Streep,Philip Seymour Hoffman,Amy Adams,Viola Davis,Alice Drummond,Audrie J. Neenan,Susan Blommaert,Carrie Preston,John Costelloe,Lloyd Clay Brown,Joseph Foster,Bridget Megan Clark,Lydia Jordan,Mike Roukis;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/doubt